dict.acceptation: 重要的；有意义的；有重大意义的；值得注意的；
有意义的事物；象征，标志；

sent.orig: Lin Yang brought a significant, significant spin, marked a significant and strong light.
sent.trans: 林淑端出显扬、显旋、显光及显强。

sent.orig: Farrowing season had highly significant effects on NSB (P<0.01), and significant effects on PBA (P<0.05)
sent.trans: 分娩季节对NSB有极显著(P<0.01)影响，对PBA有显著(P<0.05)影响。

sent.orig: Now, it was significant to me, maybe it wasn't significant to you!
sent.trans: 六年对我来说明显够长了，只是可能对你来说不够吧！

sent.orig: Small letters means significant at 0.05level, capital letters means significant at 0.01level. The same as below.
sent.trans: 不同小写字母表示0.05显著水平，不同大写字母表示0.01显著水平。下同。

sent.orig: The table lists bits ranging from the most significant bit to the least significant.
sent.trans: 表中列出了范围从最重要到最次要的位。
